== Welcome to RedTweet
RedTweet is a simple Twitter clone written in Ruby on Rails show off the Redis key-value database. 

ryo katsuma <katsuma@gmail.com>


== Requirement

1. Ruby on Rails: sudo gem install rails
2. Redis: http://code.google.com/p/redis/
3. redis-rb: sudo gem install redis


== Starting Application

Make sure the redis server is running. 
And start application:

script/server


